Chocolate Chip Cookie Dough has been making people happy ever since 1984, when fans came from all over to our Burlington, VT, Scoop Shop for a taste. Well, were dough-lighted to announce that our Non Dairy Cookie Dough is ready to bring a bunch of new smiles to a bunch of new faces. Our Flavour Gurus are always thinking of ways to make life more fun and delicious, and theyve outdone themselves this time. Our Chocolate Chip Cookie Dough Non-Dairy Ice Cream Tub has a smooth base of non-dairy vanilla ice cream with gobs of Chocolate Chip Cookie Dough mixed with delicious fudge flakes for a flavour explosion that truly has it all. Plus, its all 100% vegan and packed to the lid with euphoric goodness, all without a lick of dairy.

Our dairy-less icecream is made with almond milk and comes in responsibly-sourced packaging. Its made with Fairtrade Certified sugar, cocoa, and vanilla, so you can feel extra good about every dairy free scoop! Ready... set... dough!

Products.RichDescription:
Ben & Jerrys Non-Dairy Frozen Dessert Unfudge Our Future 458 ML
Unfudge our Future isn't just a tasty new vegan flavour you can't miss, it's a climate crisis call to action you can't ignore. Climate change is a big problem for Australia as we have some of the highest per capita emissions of CO2 in the world. That is why Ben & Jerrys has teamed up with climate leaders 350.org Australia to call on our nations leaders to Unfudge Our Future and make fossil fuels history. There is no Planet B, which is why we will also be donating a portion of the proceeds of each pint to this movement fighting for our future.

This non dairy and vegan icecream flavour is full of Chocolate and Peanut butter, Fudge Brownies & chunks of peanut butter cookie dough and with each fudgey bite is a chunky call to rebuild a clean, resilient and fair Australia! What really sets Ben & Jerrys apart from the herd is a deep commitment to social and environmental change. Ever since our co-founders started churning up ice cream back in 1978, we have been fighting for social and environmental justice and this pint is certainly no different!


Ben & Jerry's Un-fudge Our Future Non-Dairy Frozen Dessert
Ben & Jerry's Chocolate & Peanut Butter Frozen Dessert with Fudge Brownies & Chunks of Peanut Butter Cookie Dough
Ben & Jerry's includes Fairtrade certified sugar, cocoa, & vanilla
Ben & Jerry's Non-Dairy flavour creations are made with almond milk.
Ben & Jerry's is Kosher certified & Vegan
Ben & Jerrys uses responsibly sourced packaging.

BEN & JERRY`S ICE CREAM CHOCOLATE THERAPY 458 ML
Rich and creamy chocolate icecream with chunks of chocolate cookies and swirls of chocolate pudding ice cream dessert. This beyond euphoric flavour is just the cure youve been craving!

You know how sometimes you just want to scream? Sure, you could just scream, or you could grab a spoon, get a grip, and treat yourself to some primal s'cream therapy of the most sublime chocolate kind. Clinically proven by our Flavor Gurus to cure all wants and woes, Ben & Jerrys Chocolate Therapy ice cream has been a fan-favorite remedy since 2005.

Chocolate on chocolate on chocolate, its proof that you cant have too much of a good thing. Ok, sure, maybe self-control is something we all learn as children, but come on! Sometimes you just have to let loose and live. And that is exactly why we created this overly outrageous ice cream flavor. And the creamy chocolate pudding swirl? Thats just our way of saying, thanks for listening.

The healing powers of Chocolate Therapy go far beyond your freezer. Like all of Ben & Jerrys super premium ice cream pints and frozen desserts, it features only non-GMO sourced ingredients, cage-free eggs, and Fairtrade certified cocoa, sugar, and vanilla. This ice cream tub, like every pint we make, also features responsibly sourced packaging.

Chocolate Ice Cream with Chocolate Cookies & Swirls of Chocolate Pudding Ice Cream
Ice Cream includes Fairtrade certified sugar, cocoa and vanilla
All of Ben & Jerrys ice cream is made with cage-free eggs.
Ben & Jerrys Ice cream is Certified Kosher
Ben & Jerrys Ice cream uses responsibly sourced packaging

Products.RichDescription:
BEN & JERRY'S ICE CREAM SWICH UP 458 ML

Ben & Jerry's Cookie Dough S'Wich Up Ice Cream Tub is dough-licious with a base of vanilla ice cream, chocolatey cookie swirls, chocolatey cookie sandwiches AND cookie dough chunks in a legen-dairy pint!

Its our original Chocolate Chip Cookie Dough pint, with even more cookie!
Our first Cookie Dough flavour came to us as an anonymous submission by one of our fans in 1984 at our very first Scoop Shop in Burlington, Vermont USA. The folks at the Scoop Shop immediately went to work mixing up a batch of Cookie Dough ice cream. It was an instant hit. It took seven years of delicious, if painstaking, work to bring Cookie Dough to freezer aisles everywhere. Why? We had to make sure it was perfect!

Now 25 years on, we wondered how could we make it even-more-cookier! Our Flavour Guru's turned the cookie-o-meter right up to concoct this dough-licious dessert of frozen vanilla ice cream with chocolatey cookie sandwiches, a swirl of chocolatey cookies (& of course, cookie dough chunks!) in this new Cookie Dough SWich Up. We think its cookie sandwich-tastic...& hope you love this sweet sweet dessert as much as we do! Cookies & ice cream...good together, any Wich way!

We work with Fairtrade certified producers using their cocoa, sugar and vanilla. All of Ben & Jerry's ice cream is made with free-range eggs, and we always use responsibly sourced packaging.

Vanilla ice cream with a chocolatey cookie swirl, chocolatey cookie sandwiches & cookie dough chunks

Cookie Dough S'Wich Up ice cream includes Fairtrade certified cocoa, sugar and vanilla

All of Ben & Jerrys ice cream is made with cage-free eggs.

Kosher & Halal certified ice cream

Ben & Jerrys uses responsibly sourced packaging

Products.RichDescription:
Ben & Jerrys Ice Cream Chocolate Chip Cookie Dough 458 ML
Big delicious chunks of chocolate chip cookie dough surrounded by creamy vanilla icecream. It seems like such a no-brainer today, but in 1984 it was revolutionary.

The Cookie Dough you know and love started with a simple suggestion: What if you put chunks of chocolate chip cookie dough into vanilla ice cream? That was the amazing anonymous idea submitted way back in the early days of our first Burlington, Vermont, USA, Scoop Shop. We used to have a bulletin board where people could suggest new flavours for Jerry and Ben to makeand this idea stood out. The folks at the Scoop Shop immediately went to work mixing up a batch of Cookie Dough. It was an instant frozen dessert hit!

Initially, the flavour was only available at the Scoop Shop. When we decided to sell it in an ice cream tub size, we had to figure out how to get that familiar cookie-dough taste, consistency and texture at ice cream temperatures. We teamed up with Rhino Foods and, over an incredible six-year journey, we perfected the cookie dough found in our tubs today. In 1991, Cookie Dough began appearing in freezer aisles everywhere. It has remained one of our most popular and beloved flavours ever since! We get our cocoa, sugar and vanilla from Fairtrade certified producers, while Caring Dairy farmers provide all the milk and cream in this tub. Ben & Jerrys ice cream is made with non-GMO sourced ingredients and cage-free eggs. We also use responsibly sourced packaging.
Ben & Jerry's Chocolate Chip Cookie Dough Ice Cream Pint
Vanilla Ice Cream with Chunks of Chocolate Chip Cookie Dough
Includes Fairtrade certified sugar, cocoa, & vanilla
All of Ben & Jerrys ice cream is made with cage-free eggs.
Kosher certified dairy
Ben & Jerrys uses responsibly sourced packaging.

Products.FullDescription: Ben & Jerry's Ice Cream Chocolate Fudge Brownie
Products.RichDescription:
Ben & Jerrys Ice Cream Chocolate Fudge Brownie 458 ML

Fudgy chunks of brownie goodness mixed into dark and rich chocolate ice cream tub. Sounds like a frozen dessert lovers dream.

At first, thats all it was. Long ago, we were making brownie ice cream sandwiches for sale in grocery stores. Sometimes there would be broken pieces in the brownie delivery, and wed nab them for flavour experiments. What would brownie pieces taste like in chocolate icecream? Pretty good, as it turns out! That original experimental flavour eventually became the legendary ice cream concoction known as Chocolate Fudge Brownie.

Meanwhile, Ben Cohen had met Bernie Glassman, the founder of Greyston Bakery, a Yonkers, New York, USA-based company with a mission to end poverty and give back to the community. Equally important, their brownies were just so darn goodafter sampling some, Ben handwrote a note asking for two truckloads of brownie pieces. While we knew Greyston would be the ideal supplier for turning Chocolate Fudge Brownie into a ice-cream flavour sold by the tub, getting the brownies to cooperate wasnt easy. After about 25 batches of brownies and six months of work, the flavour finally debuted in 1991, and its been a hit ever since.

All the cocoa, sugar and vanilla Ben & Jerrys uses is Fairtrade certified, and the milk and cream comes from Caring Dairy farmers. Greyston Bakery, one of the largest social enterprises in the USA, continues to provide the brownies for this and all of our flavours. Our ice cream is made with cage-free eggs. And all our packaging is responsibly sourced.

Ben & Jerry's Chocolate Fudge Brownie Ice Cream Pint

Chocolate Ice Cream with Fudge Brownies

Includes Fairtrade certified sugar and cocoa

All of Ben & Jerrys ice cream is made with cage-free eggs.

Kosher certified dairy; Halal Certified

Ben & Jerrys uses responsibly sourced packaging

Products.RichDescription:
Ben & Jerrys Ice Cream Phish Food 458 ML

Chocolate ice cream with gooey marshmallow, caramel swirls and fudge fish. Its delicious, but how did this delectable ice cream tub come to be?

Ben had been pondering the lack of a good marshmallow icecream for years. Most attempts at marshmallow were wispy. You can see the white streaks, but you can't taste them, you can't feel them, you can't experience the true glorious marshmallowness of it all, Ben remembers. Well, back in 1995, we suggested to the rock band Phish that we celebrate our shared Vermont, USA, roots by creating a Phish flavor. As the wheel started turning on the collaboration, Ben saw an opportunity to solve the marshmallow conundrum once and for all.

Starting with a base of rich chocolate ice cream, he and our flavour gurus started bringing the band test tubs of the evolving concoction. We ate a lot of test tubs around the table with Phish. Weve done flavours with other artists and entities, but nobody was more involved in creating the flavor than Phish was, Jerry says. The band was instrumental, for example, in calling for caramel swirl, an addition that pushed the flavor over the top. This delicious frozen dessert is swirled with chewy marshmallow and gooey caramel in chocolate ice cream made with pure dairy cream from family farms. We poured a whole school of fish-shaped chocolatey chunks into every carton and named it Phish Food. We think it rocks!

We work with Fairtrade certified producers for cocoa, sugar and vanilla. All of Ben & Jerrys ice cream is made with non-GMO sourced ingredients and cage-free eggs. Ben & Jerrys uses responsibly sourced packaging.

Ben & Jerry's Phish Food Ice Cream Pint

Chocolate Ice Cream with Swirls of Marshmallow and Caramel and Chocolatey Fish Shaped Chunks

All of Ben & Jerrys ice cream is made with non-GMO sourced ingredients & cage-free eggs

Includes Fairtrade certified cocoa, sugar, and vanilla

Kosher certified dairy; Halal Certified

Ben & Jerrys uses responsibly sourced packaging
